{
  "entries": [
    {
      "offset": "0x1673a9",
      "back_en": "You. Nosuri, is that it?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167549",
      "back_en": "no less from the followers of a good woman.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1675f7",
      "back_en": "So he finally arrived.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1676f0",
      "back_en": "brought... other people with him. Like, a lot.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'got' rendered as 'brought'; fine."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1677e9",
      "back_en": "Hurry now, Oshtor. Your Anju awaits you.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'Seu Anju' wrong gender; Anju is female, use 'Sua Anju'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167812",
      "back_en": "Expecting Oshtor? Sorry to disappoint you.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'Yeah' dropped; minor."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167846",
      "back_en": "H-Haku!? What are YOU doing here!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16797c",
      "back_en": "sort of thing to the princess...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167a54",
      "back_en": "Hm? That man... I've seen him somewhere",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167a8e",
      "back_en": "Wh--!? YOU?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167a9a",
      "back_en": "THIS is the man for whom Anju has such affection",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167b1f",
      "back_en": "OSHTOR!! Where is my Oshtor!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167b6e",
      "back_en": "of what's happening, so he's not coming.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167cea",
      "back_en": "put something like that into the letter...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167d19",
      "back_en": "How could this be...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167d5d",
      "back_en": "farce. Stop messing around and let's take you home.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167ed1",
      "back_en": "for no one.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x167f57",
      "back_en": "as deep as forcing a family onto the streets.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1681da",
      "back_en": "Tch. Now I understand your intentions. You make",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Archaic 'vossas' fits Maroro's register."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x168209",
      "back_en": "these claims merely to confuse me!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16822c",
      "back_en": "But I will not succumb! Not before my Oshtor",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16825a",
      "back_en": "arrives, so that I may declare my most sincere feelings",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16829a",
      "back_en": "Osh... tor?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1682a6",
      "back_en": "Oshtor... Where have I heard that name...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1682d1",
      "back_en": "Nosuri! This man and his henchmen intend to separate us",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'company' rendered 'sequazes'; meaning close, splits with next line."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x168301",
      "back_en": "my Oshtor far from me!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Continuation works with prior line."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16831d",
      "back_en": "Please, you MUST help me! I can only rely upon",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16840e",
      "back_en": "her chosen one?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'intended' as 'escolhido' acceptable; fragment."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x16844e",
      "back_en": "For that is what a good woman would do!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    }
  ],
